
-- SUMMARY --
This module allows users to search for facets showing a textfield
at the very top of your Facets blocks.

-- REQUIREMENTS --
Facet API

-- HOW TO USE IT --
* Enable Facet API Search module
* From you facet block, click on "Configure facet display" contextual menu link
* Flag the "Enable contextual facets search." checkbox
* Enjoy it!

-- CONTACT --

